Objectives

- Auto allocation of students to available vacancies

- Easy application process

- Provide News 

- Verify Fees Payment

- shortlist students allocated to vacancies

- Send application status to successful students 

DashBoards

- Student 
  - logs in
  - prices of hostel h1 to h4
  - apply for desired hostel
  - View allocated room number / notify of unsuccessful applications

- Admin
  - Revoke vacancy application
  - Allocation of remaining rooms
  - Approve allocations
  - Send bulky emails to successful students

